                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for purifying tail gas of high-ammonia-diesel-ratio engine for ship",
                    "一种船舶用高氨柴比发动机尾气净化装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The device comprises an oxidation chamber, a mixing chamber, an SCR catalyst chamber and an ammoxidation catalyst chamber, an inlet of the oxidation chamber is communicated with a tail gas inlet, a gas inlet is formed in the side wall of the mixing chamber and communicated with the tail gas inlet, an oxidation catalyst is arranged in the oxidation chamber, and the tail gas inlet is communicated with the ammoxidation catalyst chamber. An SCR catalyst is arranged in the SCR catalysis chamber, a low-temperature ammoxidation catalyst is arranged in the ammoxidation catalysis chamber, and the oxidation chamber, the mixing chamber, the SCR catalysis chamber and the ammoxidation catalysis chamber are arranged in series in the flowing direction of tail gas. According to the method, part of tail gas reacts through the oxidation type catalyst, the temperature of the tail gas is properly increased, then all the tail gas passes through the SCR catalyst, remaining unburned ammonia reacts with nitric oxide generated through the reaction, the nitric oxide is removed, and the tail gas is recycled. And finally, a low-temperature ammoxidation catalyst is used for reaction to remove redundant ammonia and a very small amount of carbon monoxide, so that the emission requirement is met, the structure is simple, and the purification effect is good."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种船舶用高氨柴比发动机尾气净化装置及方法，所述装置包括氧化室、混合室、SCR催化室和氨氧化催化室，且氧化室的入口与尾气入口连通，混合室的侧壁上设有进气口与尾气入口连通，氧化室内设置有氧化型催化剂，SCR催化室内设置有SCR催化剂，氨氧化催化室内设置有低温氨氧化催化剂，氧化室、混合室、SCR催化室和氨氧化催化室沿尾气的流动方向串联设置。本发明先将一部分尾气通过氧化型催化剂进行反应，适当提高尾气的温度，再将全部的尾气通过SCR催化剂，利用剩余的未燃氨与反应生成的氮氧化物进行反应，去除氮氧化物，最后再用低温氨氧化催化剂反应去除多余的氨和极少量的一氧化碳，以达到排放要求，结构简单，净化效果好。"
                }
            ]
